<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Book Web</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background: url("/images/group5.jpeg") no-repeat center center fixed;
        background-size: cover;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .hero-container {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        max-height: 400px;
        background: rgba(238, 220, 192, 0.796); /* slight transparency for depth */
        padding: 60px 30px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: rgb(14, 61, 14);
        opacity: 70%;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #373636;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .btn-primary,
      .btn-outline-dark {
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background-color: rgb(14, 61, 14);
        opacity: 60%;
        border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
        color: white;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: rgb(14, 61, 14);
        opacity: 90%;
        border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
      }

      .btn-outline-dark:hover {
        background-color: #333;
        color: white;
      }

      @media (max-width: 576px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }

        p {
          font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .btn {
          padding: 10px 25px;
          font-size: 1rem;
        }
      }

      a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="hero-container">
      <h1>Book Web</h1>
      <p>We'll help you track your reading and choose your next book based on your mood and your favorite topics and themes.

        Simple tracking and insightful stats
        Easily track and learn about your reading habits with our wide range of charts and graphs.
        
        See how your reading develops over time and use that to help you pick better books.
        
        </p>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
        <a href="/signup">
          <button class="btn btn-primary">Sign up</button>
        </a>
        <a href="/login">
          <button class="btn btn-outline-dark">Log in</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>